modName: New Voice Type For Dark Elf
summary: Changes the playable dark elf race voice
descriptionHtml:
this is just a quick mod that changes the playable dark elf voice type that sounds more manly and better in my opinion.

There some flaws at the moment:

* no out of breath sound
* when out of you you cant hear the attack voice

Hopefully in the future ill be able to fix this some how

VIDEO

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fycy63hKt2w
author: Tomolyons
